survey_response.review_text: Dr. Swetha has been a guiding doctor from the beginning of my conception. It's through her have got the exact protocols. She communicates clearly on the problem/ health issues and treatment method. Approachable and patient friendly. I have already recommended to my friends, neighbours and family members.

Accompanied my wife as she is suffering from improper menstrual cycle. Booked an appointment through Practo app for 11:30am. Doctor came in at 11:55am. Expected doctor availability as per Practo booking, this is an improvement area.
With regards to Doctor's ********** experience and conduct, it was a positive experience.
She is knowledgeable, friendly, has patience, allows you to explain your problem patiently and prescribes practical solution.

I visited doctor for my second pregnancy. The care of the doctor was excellent. 

During my delivery it was late night full of raining. Doctor visited the hospital for delivery, the delivery of mine was unforgettable and the Dr.Shwetha saved me and my kid... Thanks for her responsibility and caring.

I recommend Dr.Shwetha for all of my friends and family.

My wife had been having irregular periods for few months. we visited aikya clinic and doctor prescribed some tests from another diagonastic centre. we got it done. she said everything looks normal and gave tablets for a course of 21 days to take every night. ***** *** ** ****** ** we visited the doctor back. she simply said continue the same tablet for 3 months untill it works. it's been more than 4 months *** **** *** ******** I don't know if anyone can be asked to wait for such long time. anyhow, considering to visit another doctor now.time and money wasted

To Doctor Swetha M.P

Before saying that you are an extraordinary doctor 👩🏻‍⚕, I want to tell you that you are an extraordinary human being. 👌 Thanks for showing so much care and concern towards my wife after the procedure and discharge from hospital. 🙏🏼

Surprising to see such doctors these days
Thanks you so much Dr Swetha.
